[h3]Prolog[/h3]
[quote]"Shroud Rising" is a renowned Stellaris mod that plunges players into the mysteries of the Shroud. Delve into its depths to uncover ancient secrets and face cosmic dangers. Navigate through ethereal realms, where every encounter unveils new enigmas. But tread carefully, for dark forces lurk within, testing your resolve. Will you harness the Shroud's power or succumb to its ominous embrace? Embark on this thrilling adventure and rewrite the fate of the galaxy![/quote]

[hr]
[h3]Since an update was sorely missed and to keep this legendary mod alive in the annals of Stellaris, I did an unofficial [b]3.12 patch to LastLeviathan's excellent [URL=//steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/2809452753]Shroud Rising[/URL] mod.[/b][/h3]
[h3][i]Detailed instructions on the latest original (3.8) [URL=//steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/2809452753]page[/URL].[/i][/h3]

[b]Note:[/b] this is a patch so you still need the original mod.

[hr]
Behold, this patch be but a spectral whisper, a mere echo in the ethereal expanse of the Shroud. 'Tis a beta, a fledgling specter yet to find its true form. tread lightly, for the mists of uncertainty cloak its every move. Changes shall materialize like phantoms, shifting and swirling in the aether.

Embrace the ephemeral nature of our journey, for the Shroud is a realm of constant flux. Expect the unexpected, as the very fabric of reality bends to our will. Your feedback, dear voyager, is the beacon that guides us through this shadowy labyrinth.

So, gather your courage and venture forth into the unknown. Within the depths of the Shroud, mysteries abound, waiting to be unraveled by intrepid souls such as yourselves. Together, let us pierce the veil and uncover the secrets that lie beyond. 🌌


